---
---
<section class="section process" id="process">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header center animate-fadeUp">
      <div class="section-tag">How It Works</div>
      <h2 class="heading-lg">Your Move in <span class="text-gradient-gold">5 Simple Steps</span></h2>
      <p style="color:var(--gray-600); max-width:520px; margin:16px auto 0;">
        We've streamlined relocation into a seamless 5-step journey so you can sit back and relax while we handle everything.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="process-steps">
      <div class="process-step animate-fadeUp">
        <div class="process-step-num">01</div>
        <div class="process-step-title">📞 Call / Request Quote</div>
        <p class="process-step-desc">Call us or fill the online form. Our expert estimates your move in minutes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step animate-fadeUp" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
        <div class="process-step-num">02</div>
        <div class="process-step-title">🔍 Free Survey</div>
        <p class="process-step-desc">Our team visits your home for a detailed survey and gives you a fixed, transparent quote.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step animate-fadeUp" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        <div class="process-step-num">03</div>
        <div class="process-step-title">📦 Professional Packing</div>
        <p class="process-step-desc">Our trained crew packs every item using premium materials — methodically, safely, efficiently.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step animate-fadeUp" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
        <div class="process-step-num">04</div>
        <div class="process-step-title">🚛 Safe Transit</div>
        <p class="process-step-desc">GPS-tracked vehicles, insured cargo, and real-time updates every step of the journey.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step animate-fadeUp" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
        <div class="process-step-num">05</div>
        <div class="process-step-title">🏠 Delivered & Settled</div>
        <p class="process-step-desc">We unload, unpack, and arrange your home. Move complete — you just walk in and live.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .process { background: var(--white); padding: 100px 0; }
  .process-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    position: relative;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }
  .process-steps::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 40px;
    left: 10%;
    right: 10%;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--blue-300), var(--gold), var(--blue-300), transparent);
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .process-step {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0 16px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .process-step-num {
    width: 80px; height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 3px solid var(--blue-200);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--blue-700);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    transition: var(--transition);
    position: relative;
  }
  .process-step:hover .process-step-num {
    background: var(--gradient-hero);
    color: var(--gold);
    border-color: transparent;
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }
  .process-step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-800);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .process-step-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .process-steps { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 40px; }
    .process-steps::before { display: none; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .process { padding: 60px 0; }
    .process-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .process-step { margin-bottom: 32px; }
  }
</style>
